{"tid":799134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯鍊金術士把「精子注入到雞蛋裡」，40天後竟誕生出「超詭異生命」震驚網路！","createTime":"2018-08-29T23:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T10:30:15.000Z","uid":52763,"like":17,"dislike":378,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"2e045441e1d7baa1b9e3daf6414c799e2d52f957","tid":799134,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T23:01:01.000Z","msg":"不知道大家有沒有聽說過「何蒙庫魯茲」（Homunculus），它是指歐洲的煉金術師所創造出的人造生命。在16世紀時，有一名叫做Pasacelsus的煉金術師寫了一份文件，上面提到如果把男人的精液注入馬的子宮中，經過40天的高溫孵化，最後就會誕生出活生生的似人生命體。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170823/1503455790188109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20170823%2F1503455790188109.jpg&h=5aa0b6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170823/1503455790188109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20170823%2F1503455790188109.jpg&h=5aa0b6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在俄羅斯一名男子將自己的精子注入雞蛋中，說自己做出了何蒙庫魯茲，在網絡上引發熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fullyu.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170823/1503455830639896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fullyu.com%2Fueditor%2Fphp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20170823%2F1503455830639896.jpg&h=f7bc5e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他在Youtube上PO出了這段影片，將自己的精液注入雞蛋中後，40天后真的從雞蛋中拉出了一個會動的奇怪生物！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Cto1DXXHAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-Cto1DXXHAc&d=Zv7mRUQtUzp1GiUzrZYPedibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8ee11440\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Cto1DXXHAc</a>"},{"pid":"061e7becb23b75cf7ae14cedd28bbd82d260d14b","tid":799134,"uid":119347,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T23:06:16.000Z","msg":"好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a351e668a2460da660e2b9ca